# Whoop Vault — local-only BLE configuration.
#
# WHOOP_BLE_MAC is populated automatically by the dashboard's Setup tab
# when you pair a strap (it scans for advertisements and writes the MAC
# here). You can also set it manually if you know the strap's MAC.
#
# Format: XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX  (uppercase hex, colon-separated)
WHOOP_BLE_MAC=
